PrecisEnactment of the EXEMPTION REGULATIONS (BEEF AND VEAL IMPORTS) which will allow those who import fresh, chilled or frozen beef and veal without a import permit to store their meat in a bonded warehouse and sell or otherwise release it to the holder of an import allocation.
